items.description:
Bertolt is a really shy boy... as shy as cute, actually, despite his height and broad shoulders. He likes long walks, spicy food, holding your hand, he will blush when you compliment him or when you tell him how colossal his d*** is. If well stimulated he might hump you mercilessly all night. Then he will cuddle you and make breakfast. So be careful ;-)

In general he's seen beside his best friend, Reiner, the jock of the school, and Bert acts for him as an aid and messenger. But some people tell there is more than a simple friendship among the two.

He's secretly in love with the school bad girl, Annie.

The model works best between 0.7 and 0.85. Comments are welcome :-P

items.name: Ultra Control & Supper Understanding|优可youkengi anime series
items.description:
优可youkengi anime系列共有的特征是极强的文本控制能力(这通常被认为是SDXL特有的性能)，不同模型之间的侧重点不同。

优可youkengi delicate anime特性：唯美的画风和更多的细节，丰富的姿势。

优可youkengi anything anime特性：较强的角色lora结合能力，较好的稳定性(更低的畸形率和更好的手)，不错的基本画风。

详细的特征描述和使用建议请参照版本描述。

关于极强的文本控制能力：

（1）只要加了fullbody几乎必出全身图（即使是横图），加了back to the viewer几乎必出背身图，（出图几乎可以无视横图还是竖图，但是不符合常规出图规律的情况下可能会增加畸形率）。

（2）在这个模型下，光凭prompt的效果几乎就可以抵得上一些lora的效果。

（3）如果你的词描述足够精确且稳定，因为极强的文本控图能力，即使切换种子这个模型画出的构图可能会非常接近。这种情况下可以尝试dynamic pose ,dynamic angle等具有一定泛化性的词汇，可以发挥这些词的实际作用，增加构图变化。

如果大家觉得满意，请多多给我返图哈~

另外关注和收藏可以收到后续版本更新和新模型的消息~

The common feature in the Youkengi Anime series is the strong text control capability, which is typically considered a unique feature of SDXL. Then, different models have different emphases.

Youkengi Delicate Anime features a beautiful art style with more details and a variety of poses.

Youkengi Anything Anime features a strong integration ability with the character Lora, good stability(Lower deformity rate and better hands), and a pleasing basic art style.

For a detailed description of the features and useage, please refer to the version descriptions.

Regarding the strong text control capability:

  1. If the word "fullbody" is included, it will almost always produce a full-body image (even if it is a horizontal image), and if "back to the viewer" is included, it will almost always produce a back-facing image. The model's ability to generate any composition you want, but won't influenced by whether the input is a horizontal or vertical image, although there may be slightly enhancing distortion when the image deviates from the usual pattern.

  2. A certain effect usually require lora to be achieved could be achieved with similar effects with just prompt alone in this model.

  3. If your word descriptions are precise and stable enough, due to the model's strong text-to-image control capability, even when switching seeds, the compositions generated by the model may be very similar. In this case, you can try using terms with certain generalization capabilities, such as "dynamic pose" or "dynamic angle" to introduce variations in the compositions.

If you are satisfied with the results, please share your feedback and provide more images.

Also, remember to follow and bookmark to receive updates on future versions and new models.

優可（Youkengi）アニメシリーズの共通の特徴は、強力なテキスト制御能力です。これは通常、SDXLの独自の特徴とされています。さらに、異なるモデルにはそれぞれ異なる重点があります。

『優可（Youkengi）デリケートアニメ』は、美しい画風で詳細が多く、様々なポーズが特徴です。

『優可（Youkengi）アニシングアニメ』は、キャラクターloraとの統合能力が高く、安定性があり（歪み率が低く、手の描写が良い）、基本的な画風も魅力的です。

詳細な特徴と使用方法については、バージョンの説明を参照してください。

強力なテキスト制御能力に関して：

「fullbody」という単語が含まれている場合、ほぼ常に全身の画像が生成されます（横向きの場合でも）。また、「back to the viewer」という単語が含まれている場合、ほぼ常に背面の画像が生成されます。このモデルでは、入力が横向きか縦向きかに関係なく、希望する構図の生成が可能ですが、通常のパターンから外れる場合にはやや歪みが増す可能性があります。

このモデルでは、特定の効果を得るためには通常ロラが必要ですが、単独のプロンプトだけでも類似の効果が得られます。

語句の説明が正確で安定している場合、このモデルの強力なテキスト制御能力により、シードを切り替えても生成される構図は非常に似通うことがあります。そのような場合には、「dynamic pose」や「dynamic angle」など、一定の一般化能力を持つ用語を使用して、構図のバリエーションを導入してみることができます。

もしご満足いただけた場合は、ぜひたくさんのフィードバックをいただけると嬉しいです。

また、フォローやブックマークをすると、今後のバージョンのアップデートや新しいモデルに関する情報を受け取ることができます。

modelVersions.name: anything ver.
modelVersions.description:
这个大模型的特点是：较强的角色lora结合能力，较好的稳定性，不错的基本画风、和极强的文本控制能力(这通常被认为是SDXL特有的性能)。

在文本控制力上，这个模型会比优可youkengi delicate anime略弱，然后侧重点不同。

一、模型特点：

1.较强的角色lora结合能力，可以和大部分的角色lora很好地结合并根据lora的风格改变角色脸型和特征，参考第三张以后的例图。由于脸部完全没有过拟，所以在脸部分辨率不足时，会容易模糊不清，这种情况推荐使用tile图生图放大。

2.较好的稳定性，不容易出现肢体崩坏，天然就有较好的手。

3.不错的基本画风，即使不配合角色lora使用，基本画风也不差，模型原本的画风参考前两张例图。

4.极强的文本控制能力，体现在对词的理解能力非常强，举例来说来体现为以下几点：

（1）只要加了fullbody几乎必出全身图（即使是横图），加了back to the viewer几乎必出背身图，（出图几乎可以无视横图还是竖图，但是不符合常规出图规律的情况下可能会增加畸形率）。

（2）在这个模型下，光凭prompt的效果几乎就可以抵得上一些lora的效果。

（3）如果你的词描述足够精确且稳定，因为极强的文本控图能力，即使切换种子这个模型画出的构图可能会非常接近。这种情况下可以尝试dynamic pose ,girl's pose等具有一定泛化性的词汇，可以发挥这些词的实际作用，增加构图变化。

二、使用方法：

1.无特别推荐的采样方法：不怎么挑，例图是使用DPM++ 2M SDE Karras来画的；

2.需要使用vae：选哪个不怎么挑，例图是使用vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.safetensors来画的；

3.推荐使用高清修复重绘幅度0.4~0.5；推荐的步数为基础25~50步，高清重绘20步。

4.如果要表现细腻的画风：推荐的放大算法为4X UltraSharp：

5.泛用性强一些R-ESRGAN 4x+，但其实模型的稳定性极强，也没什么挑。

6.唯一不建议的放大算法是latent，非常容易使画面面糊，高手要出特殊效果才需要试一下。

7.推荐的embedding：negative_hand Negative Embedding,verybadimagenegative_v1.3

如果大家觉得满意，请多多给我返图哈~

另外关注和收藏可以收到后续版本更新和新模型的消息~

The characteristics of this checkpoint are as follows: strong character Lora integration ability, good stability, decent basic art style, and extremely strong text control capability (which is typically considered a unique feature of SDXL).

In terms of text control capability, this model is slightly weaker than "Youkengi Delicate Anime" but with different emphasis.

I. Model Characteristics:

  1. Strong character Lora integration ability: It can integrate well with most character Loras and change the facial shape and features based on the Lora's style. Refer to example images from the third one onwards. Since there is no overfitting in the facial region, it may appear blurry when the facial resolution is insufficient. In such cases, it is recommended to use "tile" image generation and upscaling.

  2. Good stability: It is less prone to limb collapse and naturally produces good hands.

  3. Decent basic art style: Even without using character Lora, the basic art style is still good. Refer to the first two example images for the model's original art style.

  4. Extremely strong text control capability: It demonstrates a strong understanding of words. For example:

  • (1) If the word "fullbody" is included, it will almost always produce a full-body image (even if it is a horizontal image), and if "back to the viewer" is included, it will almost always produce a back-facing image. The model's ability to generate any composition you want, but won't influenced by whether the input is a horizontal or vertical image, although there may be slightly enhancing distortion when the image deviates from the usual pattern.

    (2) Words that usually require lora to achieve a certain effect can achieve similar effects with just prompt alone in this model.

    (3) If your word descriptions are precise and stable enough, due to the model's strong text-to-image control capability, even when switching seeds, the compositions generated by the model may be very similar. In this case, you can try using terms with certain generalization capabilities, such as "dynamic pose" or "girl's pose," to introduce variations in the compositions.

II. Usage Instructions:

  1. No specific sampling method is recommended. Examples were generated using DPM++ 2M SDE Karras.

  2. VAE usage: It doesn't matter which one you choose,but you need to choose one. Examples were generated using vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.safetensors.

  3. It is recommended to use high-definition restoration redraw factor of 0.4 to 0.5. The recommended number of basic steps is 20 to 50, followed by 20 steps of high-definition redraw.

  4. For a delicate art style, the recommended upscaling algorithm is 4X UltraSharp.

  5. For general-purpose usage, R-ESRGAN 4x+ is recommended, but in reality, the model is highly stable, so there aren't many limitations in this regard.

  6. The only upscaling algorithm not recommended is "latent" as it tends to make the image blurry. It should only be used by experts for special effects.

  7. Recommended embeddings: negative_hand Negative Embedding, verybadimagenegative_v1.3

If you are satisfied with the results, please share your feedback and provide more images.

Also, remember to follow and bookmark to receive updates on future versions and new models.

この大型モデルの特徴は、以下のとおりです：キャラクターloraとの統合能力が高く、安定性があり、基本的な画風が良く、そして非常に強力なテキスト制御能力（これは通常、SDXL独自の機能とされています）です。

テキスト制御能力に関しては、優可（Youkengi Delicate Anime）よりもやや劣る可能性がありますが、重点は異なります。

I. モデルの特徴：

  1. キャラクターロラとの統合能力が高く：ほとんどのキャラクターloraとうまく統合し、キャラクターの顔の形状や特徴をloraのスタイルに合わせて変更することができます。3枚目以降の例画像を参照してください。顔の領域にオーバーフィットがないため、顔の解像度が不足している場合はぼやけた画像になることがあります。そのような場合は、tile画像生成と拡大を使用することをおすすめします。

  2. 安定性が高く、肢体の崩壊が起こりにくく、自然な手の描写ができます。

  3. 基本的な画風が良く、キャラクターloraを使用しなくても十分なクオリティがあります。最初の2つの例画像を参照してください。

  4. 非常に強力なテキスト制御能力を持っており、単語の理解力が非常に高いです。例えば:

  • "fullbody"を含めばほぼ常に全身の画像が生成されます（横向きでも）。

  • "back to the viewer"を含めばほぼ必ず背面の画像が生成されます。（画像が横向きか縦向きかはほとんど無視されますが、一般的な画像生成のルールから外れる場合は、歪んだ結果が生成される可能性があります）。

  • このモデルでは、プロンプトのみを使用しても、一部のロラの効果にほぼ匹敵する結果が得られます。

  • 語句の説明が正確で安定している場合、強力なテキスト制御能力により、シードを切り替えてもこのモデルが描く構図は非常に似通うことがあります。そのような場合は、"dynamic pose"や"girl's pose"など、一定の一般化特性を持つ言葉を使用して、構図のバリエーションを導入してみてください。

II. 使用方法：

  1. 特に推奨するサンプリング方法はありません。例画像はDPM++ 2M SDE Karrasを使用して生成されました。

  2. VAEの使用が推奨されます。どれを選んでも問題ありません。例画像はvae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.safetensorsを使用して生成されました。

  3. 修復範囲0.4〜0.5の高解像度リストアを推奨します。基本的なステップ数は25〜50ステップで、高解像度リストアにはさらに20ステップ追加します。

  4. 繊細な画風を表現する場合、4X UltraSharpを推奨します。

  5. 汎用性が強めるにはR-ESRGAN 4x+を推奨します。ただし、このモデルは非常に安定しており、悩む必要はありません。

  6. latent以外の拡大アルゴリズムをおすすめします。latentは画像がぼやけやすくなるため、特殊な効果を得るためにのみ使用する必要があります。

  7. 推奨されるembeddingは、"negative_hand Negative Embedding"と"verybadimagenegative_v1.3"です。

もしご満足いただけた場合は、ぜひたくさんのフィードバックをいただけると嬉しいです。

また、フォローやブックマークをすると、今後のバージョンのアップデートや新しいモデルに関する情報を受け取ることができます。

modelVersions.name: delicate ver.
modelVersions.description:
这个大模型的特点是：唯美的画风，更多的细节和极强的文本控制能力(这通常被认为是SDXL特有的性能)。

在文本控制力上，他比优可youkengi anything anime略强，然后侧重点不同。

添加了剪枝模型，虽然修剪工具显示原版也没有垃圾文件，但我本人测了没发现损失。

一、模型特点：

1.唯美的画风，更多更细腻的细节，如图例所示。

2.极强的文本控制能力，体现在对词的理解能力非常强，举例来说来体现为以下几点：

（1）只要加了fullbody几乎必出全身图（即使是横图），加了back to the viewer几乎必出背身图，（出图几乎可以无视横图还是竖图，但是不符合常规出图规律的情况下可能会增加畸形率）。

（2）在这个模型下，光凭prompt的效果几乎就可以抵得上一些lora的效果，不要疑惑图例里为什么有一张高达，但他的确是只用prompt就直出的。对作者我本人来说也非常的吃惊！

（3）如果你的词描述足够精确且稳定，因为极强的文本控图能力，即使切换种子这个模型画出的构图可能会非常接近。这种情况下可以尝试dynamic pose ,girl's pose等具有一定泛化性的词汇，可以发挥这些词的实际作用，增加构图变化。

（4）可以很轻易将你想要的元素融合进人物，只用一个词，耳朵、尾巴、翅膀这些要素一个没丢，详见例图的XYZ图。

二、使用方法/生成建议：

1.无特别推荐的采样方法：不怎么挑，例图是使用DPM++ 2M SDE Karras来画的；

2.需要使用vae：选哪个不怎么挑，例图是使用vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.safetensors来画的；

2.推荐使用高清修复重绘幅度0.4；推荐的步数为基础25，高清重绘10步。

3.如果要增强光影和水彩画风：推荐的放大算法为latent，但容易使画面变糊，新手慎用：

同时增加我的两个lora效果会更明显：取Gloss_Tweaker:-1，取Edge_weaken_strengthen:1详见泳装那张图例

4.如果要表现细腻的画风：推荐的放大算法为4X UltraSharp：

5.泛用性强一些R-ESRGAN 4x+，但其实模型的稳定性很强，也没什么挑。

如果大家觉得满意，请多多给我返图哈~

另外关注和收藏可以收到后续版本更新和新模型的消息~

三、创意描述：想给大家一个能随心所欲控制出图，简单堆词也能出好图的好模型~

The characteristics of this base model are: beautiful art style and extremely strong text control capability（This is commonly considered as a unique performance of SDXL models.）.

I. Model Characteristics:

  1. Beautiful art style: Different zooming algorithms can produce two different styles of images.

  2. Extremely strong text control capability: This is reflected in its strong understanding of words. For example, it can be seen in the following points:

(1) If the word "fullbody" is included, it will almost always produce a full-body image (even if it is a horizontal image), and if "back to the viewer" is included, it will almost always produce a back-facing image. The model's ability to generate any composition you want, but won't influenced by whether the input is a horizontal or vertical image, although there may be slightly enhancing distortion when the image deviates from the usual pattern.

(2) A certain effect usually require lora to be achieved could be achieved with similar effects with just prompt alone in this model.Don't be confused about why there is an image of Gundam in the example, it was indeed generated directly with just the prompt. It's quite surprising, even for me as the author!

(3) If your word descriptions are precise and stable enough, due to the model's strong text-to-image control capability, even when switching seeds, the compositions generated by the model may be very similar. In this case, you can try using terms with certain generalization capabilities, such as "dynamic pose" or "girl's pose," to introduce variations in the compositions.

(4) You can easily integrate the elements you want into the characters using just one word. Elements like ears, tails, and wings are all preserved. Refer to the XYZ images in the example.

II. Usage Instructions:

  1. No specific sampling method is recommended. The example images were generated using DPM++ 2M SDE Karras.

  2. VAE need to be sued: No specific vae preference,but need to be used. The example images were generated using vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.safetensors.

  3. It is recommended to use a high-definition restoration redraw factor of 0.4. The recommended number of basic steps is 25, followed by 10 steps of high-definition redraw.

  4. If you want to enhance lighting and watercolor art style, the recommended zooming algorithm is "latent." It is easy to make the image blurry, so beginners should use it with caution. Additionally, combining two of my lora effects will produce more noticeable results. Set Gloss_Tweaker to -1 and use Edge_weaken_strengthen to 1. Refer to the example image of the swimsuit for details.

  5. If you want to achieve a delicate art style, the recommended zooming algorithm is "4X UltraSharp."

  6. For more general-purpose usage, R-ESRGAN 4x+ is recommended, but in reality, the model is quite stable, so there aren't many specific preferences.

この大きなモデルの特徴は、美しい画風と非常に強力なテキスト制御能力です（これは一般的にSDXLモデル固有の性能とされています）。

I. モデルの特徴:

  1. 美しい画風、例示図を参照してください。

  2. 非常に強力なテキスト制御能力は、次のような点で表れます:

（1）"fullbody"を追加すると、ほとんど常に全身のイメージが生成されます（横向きの画像でも同様です）。"back to the viewer"を追加すると、ほとんど常に背影が生成されます（画像の向きにほとんど影響を受けず、ただし通常のパターンから外れる場合は歪みが増加する可能性があります）。

（2）このモデルでは、promptだけでいくつかのloraの効果に匹敵する結果がほぼ得られます。例示図にガンダムの画像が含まれている理由について疑問に思わないでください。それはpromptだけで生成されたものです。私自身も非常に驚いています！

（3）十分に正確かつ安定したpromptがあれば、非常に強力なテキスト制御能力のため、シードを切り替えてもモデルが生成する構図は非常に似ている場合があります。この場合、"dynamic pose"、"girl's pose"などの一定の汎化性を持つ単語を試してみると、これらの単語の実際の効果を発揮し、構図の変化を増やすことができます。

（4）耳、尾、翼などの要素を簡単にキャラクターに組み込むことができます。たった1つの単語でこれらの要素を失うことなく統合します。XYZの例示図を参照してください。

II. 使用方法:

  1. 特別なサンプリング方法は推奨されていません。例示図はDPM++ 2M SDE Karrasを使用して描かれました。

  2. VAEの使用は必要: 選別は特に制約はありません。例示図はvae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.safetensorsを使用して描かれました。

  3. HD修復再描画ファクターは0.4を推奨します。基本ステップ数は25で、HD再描画は10ステップです。

  4. 光と影、水彩画風を強調する場合、推奨されるズームアルゴリズムは"latent"です。画面がぼやけやすいので、初心者は注意して使用してください。同時に、私の2つのlora効果を追加するとより明確になります。Gloss_Tweakerを-1に設定し、Edge_weaken_strengthen 1を使用します。詳細は水着の例示図を参照してください。

  5. 繊細な画風を表現したい場合、拡大アルゴリズムは4X UltraSharpが推奨されるです。

  6. 一般的な用途には、R-ESRGAN 4x+をおすすめしますが、実際にはモデルは非常に安定しており、特に具体的な好みはありません。

items.name: Ultimate Fart LoRA (Onara/おなら/オナラ)
items.description:
QUICK INFO:

  • Trained on NAI

  • Trained on 400+ images at 768x768

  • Recommended Weight: 0.7-0.8 (Feel free to experiment. When combining with other LoRAs you may get a better quality image by lowering the weight to 0.7 or 0.6.)

  • Activation Tags: Fart, Farting, Yellow Gas

  • Useful-ish Tags: Facefarting, Sittingfart, Povfart, Frontfart, Straining, Bloated Belly

IMPORTANT INFO:

I tried my hand at making a Fart LoRA, I'm relatively new to making LoRAs but I've done the best I can. I started working on this before the other two Fart LoRAs on this site were uploaded. While I named this LoRA the "Ultimate Fart LoRA" the truth is that this LoRA is a little less "ultimate" than I initially intended and a lot of things may need some trial and error (luck) to pull off.

Like with messy fingers, the gas effects have a tendency to be messy too. I really do believe this is just AI being AI and I don't know what can be done to make it more consistent. The AI does not understand what a fart cloud is, so it is common for it to mess up. You just gotta keep generating until the AI gets it right. If you've been working with AI art for a while you're probably very familiar with that already anyways. Some Checkpoints/LoRAs work well with this LoRA and some Checkpoints/LoRAs don't work well with this LoRA. I would assume that this LoRA works best with detailed anime-style models. How well it works with other styles will depend on how well that model works with this LoRA. The showcase images here were made using Kotosmix which has worked pretty well for me thus far. As I said, other models are also capable but the quality of the image will depend on which model you use.

This model will not generate onomatopoeia and other effects such as rumbling bellies which may be commonly associated with fart images. It is better if you edit that in with your editing software of choice if you desire it. It doesn't take much effort to do and it's better that way since including such images in the dataset may negatively effect the LoRA.

Lastly, this model has a habit of removing clothing that covers a characters ass for some reason. I don't know if it's because there's a large bias of naked or pantless girls in the dataset or if the AI is somehow confusing the gas effects for skin. It doesn't always happen but if it does you may want to up the priority on certain clothing or whatever else to counter this.

TAG INFO:

Tagging is split into mandatory and experimental tags. Mandatory ones are the ones you're gonna be needing to use all the time and experimental tags can be used depending on the scenario however some of them don't really work. Some of the experimental tags are necessary because fart gas effects change shape and design depending on the camera angle and scenario.

MANDATORY TAGS:

Fart, Farting - These two tags activate the LoRA and are required.

Yellow Gas - This is not mandatory but recommended. It seems this tag has an unknown effect on the gas effect which I haven't fully tested. I myself always include this tag.

USEFUL-ISH TAGS:

Facefarting - For when a character is farting on another character, typically in their face. This tag can be helpful and is recommended to use if you are generating facefart content.

Sittingfart - For when a character is farting while sitting down on something, except for when sitting on someone's face in which the facefarting tag is more appropriate. You can use both but... I don't know if that makes it better or worse. This tag seems to be helpful, but it's difficult to gauge how effective it is.

Povfart - To be used when a character's ass is directly facing the viewer and the character is not at an angle to the camera. Do not use this in normal "from behind" scenarios, only when the character's ass is directly facing the viewer or in close-up images. It seems a help... a little bit... maybe... I'd say God knows but he's abandoned me at this point.

Frontfart - To be used when the character is directly facing the viewer and is not at an angle. If the character is at any sort of angle, do not use this. This tag might not work anyways.

Straining - This tag assists in a certain facial expression where the character is pushing hard to get a fart out and is in embarrassed discomfort. Use alongside tags such as clenched teeth, wince, pain, embarrassed, v-shaped eyebrows, nose blush, etc.

Bloated Belly - This tag assists in giving a character a big, usually round, belly which is a common way of showing a character is full of gas. Use this tag alongside the big belly or huge belly tags (huge belly is probably better).

EXPERIMENTAL TAGS: (NOT RECOMMENDED)

Gasstream - When the gas effect comes out of the character's anus in a long thin stream before spreading out. This tag may not be necessary as the AI has the tendency to do a gas stream on its own even without including this tag. It may help force it if you really need it but I ultimately recommend not using this tag.

Smallfart, mediumfart, bigfart - These tags control the size of the fart. I don't think they work. I never use them in my generations.

Simplegas - Tagged onto images where the gas effects are very simple, such as only being one color. This tag may have been more useful if there were more simple gas effect images in the dataset but there's only a small minority of them which ultimately makes this tag unnecessary to use.

Sound effects, onomatopoeia - The vast majority of images in the dataset don't have text and onomatopoeia in them which means it is usually exceptionally rare for them to show up during image generation. For that reason, adding these tags is unnecessary and it may do more harm than good. If you want images to actually have onomatopoeia you are much better off opening your editing software of choice and adding them yourself. Like with simplegas, it would've been more useful if there were more images in the dataset with onomatopoeia. Do not use.

Unorthodoxgas - An attempt to prevent messy gas effects by tagging the images where the gas effects are wonky. This tag does not work.

Green gas, Brown gas, Orange gas - For differently colored gas effects. These tags do not work.

items.name: Casual Poses
items.description:
Casual/everyday activity poses for controlnet.

I am open to suggestions for what other categories to add to this so-far boring list.

Please read the version description for notes that are specific to the version.

In the .zip files: example generation plus the .png to use in openpose, canny and depth models. Added .json for openpose too so you can make modifications to the pose file. They're not always very functional though.

To do list

  • Sleeping outside of bed (slumped in a chair, head down on a table, curled up on the floor) -- suggested by 0ryan -- DONE

  • Interacting with pets (petting a cat, walking a dog, feeding fish, lizard on shoulder) -- suggested by 0ryan

  • Playing games (holding a controller, moving a chess piece, dealing cards, etc) -- suggested by 0ryan

  • Yoga

  • Reading

  • Office/computer work

  • ...

Additional notes

  • Use attributes like "from_behind", "from_below", "from_above", or "from_side" in your prompt to create the angles you are looking for. Describe accurately what you want to see (such as "stomach", "thighs", "back" etc.) to help "turn" a character.

Version notes

  • As always, aspect ratio is crucial to the output.

  • Phone: Use canny for most flexibility. Canny fills the blank spots very well and you can easily edit the file to make changes to the template. Openpose (full) also works pretty well in this one as it helps getting the fingers right. The .json is practically useless for this version. If you want to generate something that is close to the example picture (an athletic woman with long hair), use depth or run the example picture through the normal map preprocessor and model. Useful keywords: smartphone, holding smartphone, selfie, phone, mirror selfie, etc.

  • Dozing: Would suggest a combination of OpenPose (weight 1.0) and depth (weight 0.3-0.8) in multi ControlNet here. OpenPose alone is not enough in most cases. Depth alone might suffice in most cases though.

  • Presenting: I included "(presenting a blank_page:1.5)" in my prompts and it usually got the job done in keeping the object a blank white space (but responding to the lighting of the scene). Pose 1 is a little tricky to pull off. Try not to describe the upper body of the character holding the poster/painting/document too much as parts of it would then show up ON the object. Some odd looking results. You can combine depth and canny (to improve fingers) for pose 1. Depth is doing the heavy lifting here though. With just canny you will not get the right results. The contents of the presentation can easily be generated/modified via inpainting. Paint a mask over the poster/painting/photo, "only masked" instead of "whole picture", 512x512 and a denoising strength of 0.6 to 0.75 usually gets the job done.

All pictures were generated with the Comimicry model (https://civitai.com/models/105172). DPM++ 2M Karras sampler.

Lora used: 3D Rendering Style (https://civitai.com/models/73756/3d-rendering-style) v1.4.1

Prompt and other generation data: see attached pictures.

From a hero to your school's sports teacher. Your favorite character has found a new passion in teaching!

Recommended Strength of Other Mixed LoRA / LyCORIS: 0.4 - 0.8

Inspiration for this came from watching a sports anime that a friend recommended. You can now get AI to turn people into that dreamy-looking PE teacher! You can prompt NSFW although it might be more for the fujyoshi creators as there was a lot more "male + male" artwork for this concept. Realistic pictures were overall just pretty SFW though. As seen from the last sample image, it will give female characters more male traits if you try mixing. Enjoy your generations!

items.name: Peugeot 907
items.description:
If you like my Loras, you can buy me beer here (https://ko-fi.com/djo226) or you can subscribe to my Patreon and get exclusive models (public showcase preview) and support me.

The Peugeot 907 was a concept car built by Peugeot. Unveiled at the 2004 Paris Motor Show, the car was created by styling chief Gérard Welter and designer Jean Christophe Bolle Reddat to celebrate the closure of the firm’s 40-year-old design centre at La Garenne and the opening of the new centre at Vélizy.

The car was never designed to go into production, but was intended to be a prototype featuring the new design techniques by Peugeot.

The engine is mounted just behind the front wheels, and side exhausts exit behind each of the front wheels. Unlike many concepts, the 907 can be driven like any production car. Under the bonnet, two 3.0-litre V6 engines are combined to form a 500BHP V12.

The monocoque body is made of carbon fiber and the car uses a double-wishbone suspension all round, while the sequential-shift transmission distributes power to the rear wheels. The arcing windscreen continues upwards to form the roof, while the bonnet has a see-through perspex insert that reveals the engine’s 12 intake trumpets.
